  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An simple-blind, randomized study, to evaluate the efficacy and safety of complete closure
      with clips of mucosal defects after endoscopic mucosal resection (EMR) of large
      non-pedunculated colorectal lesions (≥ 2 cm) as prophylaxis of delayed bleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
